00:43:08.040 --> 00:43:12.150
and once you see
something materializing,

00:43:12.150 --> 00:43:16.630
you quit your job,
or you just say, OK,

00:43:16.630 --> 00:43:18.990
the only way to move
forward with this

00:43:18.990 --> 00:43:24.310
is if I disconnect, detached,
breakup, and start my new life.

00:43:24.310 --> 00:43:27.640
And it's a character,
